Texts.Chs: 高级与门 (2个输入节点，无锁存器)
Texts.Eng: Advanced And Gate (2 Inputs, No Latch)

Texts.Chs: 这个与门具有2个输入节点，但没有内置锁存器。
Texts.Eng: An /'And'/ gate with 2 inputs and a built-in Not Gate, but no built-in Data Latch.

Texts.Chs: 和普通的与门不一样，但是我觉得有锁存器会更方便一些。
Texts.Eng: Not all that different from a normal AND Gate, but the built-in Not Gate is convenient.

Texts.Chs: 和普通通通的与门不一样，但是我觉得有锁锁锁存器会更方便一些。
Texts.Eng: Not all that different from a normal AND Gate, but the built-in Not Gate isss convenient.
